-- drop EXTERNAL TABLE [dim].[Warehouse]
CREATE  EXTERNAL TABLE [dim].[Warehouse]
WITH
(
	LOCATION = 'gold/Dimensions/Warehouse', 
	DATA_SOURCE = datalake1pgc,
	FILE_FORMAT = ParquetFileFormat
) AS 
SELECT 
ROW_NUMBER () OVER (ORDER BY idWarehouse, fromDate) idSkWarehouse,
w.*,  --, CAST(CAST(deltaDate as nvarchar) AS datetime2)
CAST('1990-01-01' AS datetime2) AS fromDate,
CAST('9999-01-01' AS datetime2) AS toDate ,
1 isCurrent
FROM
[SilverlessSTG].[etl].[vw_dim_Warehouse] as w
